&lt;p&gt;为了提防水逆带来的霉运，小美特地找来了这个小程序，「水逆转运符」，这个小程序真的是很有趣哦。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://qstatic.zuimeia.com/img/article/6266/809155d98b655887268d3b787782b34c_1242x2208.PNG?imageMogr/v2/gravity/South/crop/!1242x2208-0-0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;113&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://qstatic.zuimeia.com/img/article/6266/8c75fe55874def2101b936f47531a11e_1242x2208.PNG?imageMogr/v2/gravity/South/crop/!1242x2208-0-0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;112&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这个小程序最有趣的地方，不仅仅是自己能够有一种心理暗示，来驱散水逆，还能够自制各种符条，来霸占朋友圈。操作简单，玩起来非常开心。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://qstatic.zuimeia.com/img/article/6266/c841e2f186b34b460901b59dce719d1c_1242x2208.PNG?imageMogr/v2/gravity/South/crop/!1242x2208-0-0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;113&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://qstatic.zuimeia.com/img/article/6266/b533c54dfc9e00609c2be9381792f5bd_1242x2208.jpg?imageMogr/v2/gravity/South/crop/!1242x2208-0-0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;112&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;如果真的觉得水逆或者星座运势对自己有影响的朋友，那么十分必要试试这款小程序。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://qstatic.zuimeia.com/img/article/6266/016e5e3eba84164f3be1be3751709d56_1200x700.jpg?imageMogr/v2/gravity/South/crop/!1200x700-0-0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;343&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
