&lt;p&gt;这款小程序「幸运云」，简直是一个玄学的大集合。里面感觉各种神仙，各种佛祖，各种宗教，全都有。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://qstatic.zuimeia.com/img/article/6266/b7da9e381b9f5290d200bfeda7d218da_1242x2208.PNG?imageMogr/v2/gravity/South/crop/!1242x2208-0-0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;113&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; /&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://qstatic.zuimeia.com/img/article/6266/8c2aaf87b18d58211955ef76f13c4e49_1242x2208.PNG?imageMogr/v2/gravity/South/crop/!1242x2208-0-0&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; width=&quot;112&quot; height=&quot;200&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
